            <description><![CDATA[<div class="figure-media figure-media-gallery figure-media-gallery-overlay js-figure-media-gallery js-figure-media-gallery-overlay">
         <div class="figure-media-gallery-slide"><div class="figure-media-gallery-img"><img class="article-rotator-img lazyload" data-src="/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/2023-01/ZB_0109_CJ_doc7oehpiy60afrjntcgwg_08224310_yinlu.jpg?itok=Rx-Cg9ik" alt="" data-caption="　王鸿薇在台北市第三选区立委补选中当选，不过得票率不如预期。（王鸿薇脸书）　吴怡农被民进党败选的黑金等因素拖累，小负国民党候选人王鸿薇5%。（吴怡农脸书）" src="https://www.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/2023-01/ZB_0109_CJ_doc7oehpiy60afrjntcgwg_08224310_yinlu.jpg?itok=Rx-Cg9ik" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><div class="tint"></div></div>
